data.description: LOCATION - LOCATION - LOCATION ! Upon arrival, you will notice the lush landscaping and painted driveway. This popular 3/2 Cottage/Ranch AMARILLO is close to LAKE SUMTER LANDING and BROWNWOOD with all the shopping and restaurants you heart desires. Enjoy your Morning cup of java or simply the serenity of sitting in the covered front porch. Entering, you notice the spacious living area with vaulted ceiling, crown molding, plantation shutters and view of the private back yard - no kissing lanai here - with screened covered lanai and attached large 12 x 24-foot birdcage. The home features a split bedroom floor plan and an indoor laundry room with washer & dryer and storage cabinets. The master bedroom offers two walk-in closets and an en-suite bathroom with tiled shower and double sink vanity.  The guest bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home and are separated by a pocket door for privacy with a guest bathroom in between - both offer closets. The front guest bedroom features a queen size Murphy bed with bookshelves.  The kitchen offers Granite countertops and black appliances. Like doing home projects? You will love the garage with workbench, storage cabinets and painted floor. The home features a newer roof (2013) and HVAC (2010).   Tax line reflects property tax only! CDD amount includes $1,282.50 bond payment and $446.21 VCDD Maintenance. TURNKEY OPTION available.
